kg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkeaa.edu.hk%2Ftc%2FHKDSE%2Fadmin%2Fexam_centres%2Fexam_centres.html&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=29993484\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkeaa.edu.hk/tc/HKDSE/admin/exam_centres/exam_centres.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">建議大家自行<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">印有QRcode單張<br />\n+<br />\n派選民登記表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n可循以下途徑索取表格：<br />\n1。各區民政事務處<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.had.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcontact_us%2Fcomment_c.htm&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=cd741d44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.had.gov.hk/tc/contact_us/comment_c.htm</a><br />\n2。公共屋邨辦事處（大家樓下就有）<br />\n3。選舉事務處地址：</span><br />\n-&gt;香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓<br />\n-&gt;九龍九龍灣展貿徑1號九龍灣國際展貿中心13樓<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">只要在2020年7月25日或以前年滿18歲，今年5月2日前可登記做選民\n\n18歲生日快樂 即刻登記做選民</code></pre><br />\n選民登記填表機<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=ae9758b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote</a><br />\n地方選區選民新登記申請表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=bb996a34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n選民資料網上查閱系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F6f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=a1a5a51e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/M8STBFS.jpg\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/a8T7y6C.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"93bc1309b2cb315690b7034d35087e8d99b43deb","tid":1936174,"uid":94388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔係止係黃碧雲，好撚多泛民缺席"},{"pid":"7bec5c04c6c127a6b1d2c9813cfff768952f806d","tid":1936174,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b157dc3d196eae325ee8c097d2693e43bdedd0","tid":1936174,"uid":12798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"喺我記憶所及<br />\n黃碧雲最撚出色莫過于17年政改投票<br />\n投票嘅時候班保皇黨抗議離場<br />\n條撚𨳒話要點人數<br />\n慌死d保皇黨返唔到入嚟投票咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有網落廿三條嗰時<br />\n黃毓民係煲底就掌聲雷動<br />\n佢出去就畀人圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住人哋發言話佢哋民主派嘅不是<br />\n就發爛渣叫點人數打人哋發言<br />\n無建樹都算啦又唔話得<br />\n典型嘅販民、大佬文化<br />\n總之販民做嘜都唔撚𨳒得尤其係民主黨<br />\n哩班撚𨳒咩好事都無做過<br />\n都唔知憑咩要人含<br />\n重要唔含你就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}